title: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description:
Description: An exception is thrown when exporting data from the attached report.
Steps to reproduce: 
1. Open the report that contains a table with highlights or maps.
2. Attempt to export the data in the table.
OB: When attempting to export data from a table containing highlights or maps, an exception is thrown.
EB: The data in the table should be exported successfully without any exceptions being thrown.
SR:
1. Open the report.
2. Navigate to the table with highlights or maps.
3. Click on the export data option.
4. Verify that the data is exported correctly and no exceptions are encountered.
